1. *Napolju* je divan dan (It is a beautiful day outside).
2. Ona voli da se šeta *napolju* (She likes to walk outside).
3. On je već dugo vani *napolju* (He has been outside for a long time).
4. Mi smo već dugo *napolju* (We have been outside for a long time).
5. Moja sestra je često *napolju* (My sister is often outside).
6. Deca vole da se igraju *napolju* (The children like to play outside).